904
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,640
when she married him.

905
00:42:00,090 --> 00:42:01,730
It really is precious material.

906
00:42:01,970 --> 00:42:03,470
Grandmother gave it to Zhonglin,

907
00:42:03,470 --> 00:42:05,160
